  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dd6\u0db4 \u0da1\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u0da8 \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Great victory for Lajwala Co-op polls",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Samagi Jana Balawewa has won a landslide victory in the multi-service cooperative elections in the upper echelons of Galle. The election to elect a Board of Directors for the next three years of the Upper Lale Multipurpose Co-operative Society was held today (26) at the Co-operative Headquarters.",
        "Out of the 12 Co-operative Localities belonging to the Co-operative Society, 83 members were elected to the General Assembly and the majority of the General Assembly representatives were elected from the Samagi Jana Balawegaya Party.",
        "It is noteworthy that all the seven members of the Board of Directors have been elected from the General Assembly and the Samagi Jana Balawegaya is from the party."
      ],
